data.description: Introducing a 2022 New Construction Home that has UnParalleled Luxury at Over 3700 Square Feet WITH BRAND NEW HUGE HEATED POOL & Spa with Waterfall in the Highly Desirable Bexley Neighborhood on a Conservation Lot. Where Every Detail Has Been Meticulously Thought Through. Builders Are Asking Over 1 Million for Just the Home Not Including Upgrades or POOL. This Home is Steal and Completely Move In Ready and Sits on One of the Largest Lots at . 27 Acres. The Sellers Have Done All the Work For You And Spent Over $200k in Builder Upgrades and then Another $250k Additional After Closing to Make This Home One of a Kind. Whole House Solar Panels that Are Fully Paid Off! Oversized 3 Car Garage as well! Adorable Front Porch with Brick Pavers Perfect for Relaxing Evenings or Enjoying the Morning Coffee. High Ceilings and Today's Popular Grays and Whites Fill the Walls and Trim. One of the Most Sought After Layouts with a Front Formal Den with Double Door Access and Two Bedrooms with Hall Bathroom All Located in the Front Section Wing of the Home. You Will Be the Envy of All Your Friends with this DREAM Gourmet Modern Kitchen Highly Upgraded with Floor to Ceiling Shaker Style Cabinetry, Quartz Countertops, Top of the Line SS Appliances (High-End Refrigerator, Double Oven, 5-Burner Gas Stove-Top, Range Hood), Backsplash, Expansive Island with Generous Space for 4 Seater Breakfast Bar and BONUS "Morning Kitchen/Desk Area" for Coffee Bar with HUGE Walk in Pantry! There Are Kitchens the Size of this Pantry. Seperate Eat In Area/Dining Room Faces the Back of the Home and Has Beautiful Views of the Newly Finished Pool and Backyard Space. Family Room is Oversized and Offers a Variety of Different Options for Furniture Placement. Sliding Door Access to Newly Finished Fully Enclosed Screened Birdcage with Extended Brick Paver Patio with Pool Fence, Astroturf Green Space for Fur Friends, tot lot Playground or Game of Bags and The Showstopper of Them All is The Expansive 15x30 in Ground Swimming Pool with Spa, 4 Waterfall Features with Lights! This Home Really is an Entertainer's Dream Home! Your Guests Won't Want to Leave. Almost Forgot to Mention the Home Backs Up to a Conversation Lot so No Backyard Neighbors and the Yard is Completely Fenced in as well with Additional Dog Run Area. Primary Bedroom Suite is Right Off of the Family Room and Separate From All Other Bedrooms and Features Double Sink Vanities with an Enormous Glass/Tile Enclosed Walk in Shower and Two Separate Walk in Closets with Custom Closet Organizer Cabinets for Added Storage. The Fourth Bedroom with Private Ensuite Bathroom is the Perfect In-Law Suite and is Tucked Away in Another Wing of the Home with the Laundry Room and Mudroomwith Space for Built-in Shelving Storage if Desired. The 2nd Floor is a BONUS Room that Can Be Used as a 2nd Office, Movie Theater Room, 5th Bedroom, Gym. The Possibilities are Endless! Additional Features of the Home Include All Bedrooms/Office Have Hardwired Internet Ports, Whole House is on a Dual Zone Air Conditioning System, Tankless Water Heater System, Surround Sound Pre Wire on 2nd Floor, Wifi Access Point Throughout Entire Home and so much more. This Home Does Not Disappoint and Neither Will the Community that Features State of the Art Facility with Fitness Center, 2 Resort Style Community Pools, Dog Park, 26 Miles of Walking and Biking Nature Preserve Trails, Parks, Playgrounds and TOP Rated Schools. Great location!
